data.title: midAMerica
data.text:
DX-midAMerica has been here since 1981. Quite a few AM radio stations have gone silent since! Financial, growth of FM, dumping one frequency and moving to another. When you look at what you've logged through the years and even decades of this great hobby, look at this listing which I'm sure is not complete, though still pretty accurate. Data used here is from FCC, my radio loggings, old record survey collections. If you have any to add along with a note or two, feel free to add to this list. You will be credited. Updated: November 18,2019 info@DX-midAMerica.com

This listing focuses only on stations in midAMerica with a very few outside the area. Losses incurred from PEI, Nova Scotia, and British Columbia are included!

GONE, but not forgotten, but they gave great radio and gave us all good memories!
